OL,3,CHow to see tonight's worm moon in the
OL,4,CUK, as blood moon visible around the
OL,5,Cworld
OL,7,FParts of the world were treated to a
OL,8,Frare "blood moon" today as a total
OL,9,Flunar eclipse graced the sky.
OL,11,FA total lunar eclipse takes place when
OL,12,Fthe Earth passes directly between the
OL,13,Fsun and a full moon, casting a shadow
OL,14,Fover its surface and causing it to
OL,15,Fappear red or dark orange.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/5
