PN,31902
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1772658365
OL,3,CHow to see tonight's worm moon in the
OL,4,CUK, as blood moon visible around the
OL,5,Cworld
OL,7,FThe phenomenon was visible during the
OL,8,Flate hours of Tuesday evening in
OL,9,FAustralia, New Zealand, Tokyo, the
OL,10,FPhilippines, India, and China, and the
OL,11,Fearly hours of US cities like New
OL,12,FYork, Los Angeles, Chicago and New
OL,13,FOrleans.
OL,15,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,16,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,17,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,18,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/5
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
