PN,31904
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1772658365
OL,3,CHow to see tonight's worm moon in the
OL,4,CUK, as blood moon visible around the
OL,5,Cworld
OL,7,FWhile the blood moon was not visible
OL,8,Ffrom the UK, Brits had a chance to
OL,9,Fspot the "worm moon" - the March full
OL,10,Fmoon - at its fullest point this
OL,11,Fmorning, with another opportunity to
OL,12,Fsee it Tuesday night.
OL,14,FThe worm moon is thought to get its
OL,15,Fname from earthworms starting to
OL,16,Femerge from the soil at this time of
OL,17,Fyear as the weather becomes warmer.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/5
